These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, ambient, country, soul
1. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is between the fan of pop and the fan of ambient##2
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | pop | soul | ambient | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
House: modern, palace, wooden, farmhouse
1. the modern house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the palace house is in an odd position##4
3. the palace house is on the left or right of the modern house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| House   | palace | modern | farmhouse | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, chestnut, aquamarine, blood-red
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
2. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes chestnut##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Color   | turquise | blood-red | aquamarine | chestnut |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
