1. the italian is on the left or right of the colombian##3
2. the chinese is in an even position##4
3. the argentine is between the colombian and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Nationality   | italian | colombian | argentine | chinese |

