.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, musical, adventure
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | mystery | adventure | horror |

