2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts | sports | thriller |

