.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, november, august
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | august | april | november | december |

