.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, swisher, chaman, oliveros
1. the swisher-smoker is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
3. the chaman-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the prince-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | chaman | oliveros | swisher | prince |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile, car, boat
1. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Transport   | helicopter | boat | car | snowmobile |

 